                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Iddings</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Rome</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-08-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 1, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Iddings inquires if he shall give testimony against a pickpocket, which is
                    desired by an Italian court.)</p>
            </div>
